description: New Frontier Energy, Inc., an independent energy company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, development, and production of natural gas and crude oil. Its operations are conducted in the continental United States, principally in the Denver Julesberg Basin. The company was formerly known as Storage Finders.com and changed its name to New Frontier Energy, Inc. in March 2001. New Frontier Energy, Inc. was founded in 2000 and is based in Denver, Colorado.
